  <brief_title>Study to Compare the Effects of Two Dosages of Tolvaptan in Congestive Heart Failure Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Multi-Center, Double-Blind Study to Compare the Effects of 30mg Qd Versus 15 Mg Bid of Tolvaptan in Congestive Heart Failure Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
